Cell07PNs: 40 Sample Projection Neurons from Jefferis, Potter et al 2007

These R lists (which have additional class neuronlist) contain 40 traced olfactory projection neurons from Jefferis, Potter et al 2007 that have been transformed onto the IS2 template brain (Cachero, Ostrovsky et al 2010).

References

Jefferis G.S.X.E., Potter C.J., Chan A.M., Marin E.C., Rohlfing T., Maurer C.R.J., and Luo L. (2007). Comprehensive maps of Drosophila higher olfactory centers: spatially segregated fruit and pheromone representation. Cell 128 (6), 1187--1203. http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.cell.2007.01.040

Cachero S., Ostrovsky A.D., Yu J.Y., Dickson B.J., and Jefferis G.S.X.E. (2010). Sexual dimorphism in the fly brain. Curr Biol 20 (18), 1589--601. http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.cub.2010.07.045

See also

head.neuronlist, with.neuronlist

Other nat-data: MBL.surf, kcs20
